1442962,"uid":272271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a154620cbb357c584a7edbcf9aee2ec774018cd","tid":1442962,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:56:39.000Z","msg":"推 非常同意<br />\n但點樣解決呢個問題？ 一旦拆晒舊野好難建返<br />\n但唔拆舊野又冇位貼新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:10:52.000Z","msg":"要有人力，係d多人的地區街坊group提出要重建的需要性先，集齊一group人 約時間一齊落去拆<br />\n重建初期一定無依家咁滿咁大，但劃左個鋪排雛型先，等其他人跟住貼/做decoration <br />\n<br />\n重建一定要痛苦，但要諗保持現貌究竟有咩用。如果本身已經無左用途的話，即係拆左他其實唔係咁大損失"},{"pid":"03f70e9e068cbeea8fe991f70d7c880a1cf43e50","tid":1442962,"uid":272271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:16:47.000Z","msg":"參考 機場726<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JNSfy1S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJNSfy1S.jpg&h=9a605ec8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a873c87beb7928dbd86177f3868916eca19ca172","tid":1442962,"uid":298893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:17:32.000Z","msg":"我有睇，經過果陣仲同啲義工打氣"},{"pid":"5c5dcf62345a7efb4cbc918fd4665ca28cac783f","tid":1442962,"uid":265171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"支持重建計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956743de6e71b8fc5798e8dc4acfdcf7631e3633","tid":1442962,"uid":268801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:19:01.000Z","msg":"撕紙狗有時係做緊好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔撕 我點貼"},{"pid":"f9e90cb6244ba70674df16beae51d62e33f50ce4","tid":1442962,"uid":71831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"岩 連儂要重建了"},{"pid":"173cecef133c988bb20295f2b959750f0ea6d92c","tid":1442962,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"有人"},{"pid":"2ceddf6a64768fc4bc9abc93b4810a7b100a3cb4","tid":1442962,"uid"